"16:38:16" : {s: 16, a: 38, w: 16, r: "نوس", t: "ٱلنَّاسِ", l: "نَّاس", lc: 241, tl: "l-nāsi", lb: "মানুষ, মানবজাতি ",e: "(of) the mankind", b: "লোকদের (এমনও আছে)", f: 92, rm: "to swing, halt in a place, move, toss. Mankind, people, others, men."},
