"16:42:2" : {s: 16, a: 42, w: 2, r: "صبر", t: "صَبَرُوا۟", l: "صَبَرَ", lc: 58, tl: "ṣabarū", lb: "ধৈর্য, নিষ্ঠার সাথে চেস্টা করা ",e: "(are) patient", b: "তারা ধৈর্য ধারণ করেছে", f: 13, rm: "to bind, be patient or constant, endure patiently, steadily adhere to reason and command, restrain from what reason and law forbid, restrain from manifesting grief, agitation and impatience. The word being the contrary of jaza (manifestation of grief and agitation)."},
